00:01:26.003 --> 00:01:28.379
nobody understood Her value.

00:01:30.545 --> 00:01:32.461
Nobody saw

00:01:32.586 --> 00:01:37.795
that She was such a great spiritual personality.

00:01:38.295 --> 00:01:40.545
Only through Sahaja Yoga

00:01:41.045 --> 00:01:43.212
you can understand that She was

00:01:43.461 --> 00:01:46.254
a very great personality

00:01:46.503 --> 00:01:50.545
who gave birth to Christ.

00:01:56.129 --> 00:02:00.379
It is very unfortunate

00:02:01.795 --> 00:02:03.837
that She was not respected,

00:02:05.170 --> 00:02:08.586
specially in the Islamic world.

00:02:09.295 --> 00:02:10.503
Because of that,

