Christians - Christians won't respect Hindus.

00:03:35.254 --> 00:03:37.711
I mean it's a funny thing that's going on.

00:03:39.129 --> 00:03:41.003
They all are for God

00:03:41.837 --> 00:03:44.337
and for God's work and His love.

00:03:45.461 --> 00:03:48.045
Despite that, there's no respect.

00:03:48.837 --> 00:03:49.878
There's no love.

00:03:51.129 --> 00:03:53.586
On the contrary, they're all quarrelling, fighting,

00:03:53.753 --> 00:03:57.545
killing everywhere.

00:03:59.045 --> 00:04:00.087
It's very sad

00:04:01.295 --> 00:04:04.170
that in the name of religion and God,

00:04:04.461 --> 00:04:08.753
people should become so cruel and so absurd.

00:04:10.878 --> 00:04:12.212
This is the only solution-

00:04:14.170 --> 00:04:16.379
