All human beings can get Self Realization.

00:04:50.670 --> 00:04:54.586
Whether they are from Africa,

00:04:55.379 --> 00:04:58.837
England, America, India, anywhere.

00:05:00.212 --> 00:05:02.212
They all can get their miraj.

