Why should human beings fight

00:05:18.337 --> 00:05:20.129
- that, too, in the name of religion.

00:05:20.545 --> 00:05:21.962
In the name of God,

00:05:24.420 --> 00:05:26.212
Christ came on this Earth

00:05:26.545 --> 00:05:28.586
just to create oneness of religion,

00:05:29.503 --> 00:05:33.379
but even the Christians, they only started fighting,

00:05:34.170 --> 00:05:35.670
dominating others.

00:05:36.295 --> 00:05:39.295
It's a big world of turmoil,

00:05:39.920 --> 00:05:44.170
where everybody is fighting in the name of God

00:05:44.379 --> 00:05:47.045
and in the name of religion.

00:05:48.295 --> 00:05:50.711
So our religion is global,

00:05:51.753 --> 00:05:53.129
is one religion.

00:05:53.795 --> 00:05:56.003
We respect all the Deities,

00:05:57.545 --> 00:05:59.545
all the Gods and Goddesses

00:06:00.711 --> 00:06:04.045
- respect Them and worship Them.

00:06:04.962 --> 00:06:08.711
We are not so stupid

00:06:09.837 --> 00:06:13.254
not to understand that They are all one.

00:06:14.503 --> 00:06:16.461
Also, after getting Realization,

00:06:16.795 --> 00:06:20.045
you realize that all these exist

00:06:20.254 --> 00:06:22.670
on our central nervous system.

00:06:23.337 --> 00:06:25.670
They exist on our chakras.

00:06:26.753 --> 00:06:29.503
They are not there

00:06:31.170 --> 00:06:34.670
just because people have told us in history and all that,

00:06:34.962 --> 00:06:36.753
but actually in that's a fact,

00:06:37.962 --> 00:06:40.254
that all of them are there together,

00:06:40.670 --> 00:06:43.837
working out the resurrection of the whole world.

00:06:44.920 --> 00:06:47.670
So the greatest thing that Christ has done

00:06:48.170 --> 00:06:49.962
is the resurrection part

00:06:50.670 --> 00:06:54.295
and in this resurrection, He suffered a lot.

00:06:54.503 --> 00:06:57.420
He had to go through lots of ordeals

00:06:57.962 --> 00:07:00.920
and then His body itself was resurrected.

00:07:02.586 --> 00:07:05.212
On the same lines, Sahaja Yoga is working out

00:07:05.962 --> 00:07:08.170
- that you get your Realization

00:07:08.670 --> 00:07:10.212
means your resurrection.

00:07:11.420 --> 00:07:13.545
All your wrong ideas disappear.

00:07:14.628 --> 00:07:16.711
All your nonsense disappears

00:07:17.379 --> 00:07:19.087
and nothing but love,

00:07:19.795 --> 00:07:22.628
understanding comes in.

